<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>시대별 클래식 음악가와 채팅하기</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7efe5, #fff8e7, #f3e1c8);
      color: #3b2f2f;
    }

    .screen {
      display: none;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .active {
      display: block;
    }

    .hero {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto 26px;
      background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.92);
      border: 4px double #a87932;
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 28px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(90, 55, 20, 0.18);
    }

    .main-title {
      font-size: 40px;
      color: #5b2c1f;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .era-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 24px auto;
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255, 253, 246, 0.94);
      border: 3px solid #d4af37;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .era-title {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 27px;
      color: #6b3f16;
    }

    .era-desc {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #5a4a3a;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .musician-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fffaf0;
      border: 3px solid #b8860b;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.25s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-7px) scale(1.03);
      background: #fff1c7;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 132px;
      height: 132px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 4px solid #d4af37;
      background: #eee;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 12px 0 5px;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #4a2515;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      margin: 5px 0;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .chat-container {
      max-width: 840px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fffdf6;
      border: 4px solid #8b5a2b;
      border-radius: 26px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .chat-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5b2c1f, #8b5a2b);
      color: white;
      padding: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .chat-header img {
      width: 74px;
      height: 74px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid #f7d774;
      object-fit: cover;
      background: #eee;
    }

    .chat-header h2 {
      margin: 0 0 5px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .chat-header p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .warning {
      background: #fff3cd;
      color: #5b4200;
      padding: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-bottom: 2px dashed #d4af37;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .quick-buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      background: #fffaf0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e1c16e;
    }

    .quick-buttons button {
      border: 2px solid #b8860b;
      background: #fff6d8;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4c2d13;
    }

    .quick-buttons button:hover {
      background: #f8df8a;
    }

    .chat-box {
      height: 400px;
      padding: 20px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      background: #fdf6e3;
    }

    .message {
      max-width: 80%;
      padding: 13px 16px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
      white-space: pre-line;
    }

    .bot {
      background: #efe1c6;
      border: 2px solid #b8860b;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .user {
      background: #d9ecff;
      border: 2px solid #6aa5d7;
      margin-left: auto;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .chat-input {
      display: flex;
      padding: 15px;
      background: #fffaf0;
      border-top: 2px solid #d4af37;
    }

    .chat-input input {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      border: 2px solid #b8860b;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .chat-input button,
    .back-btn {
      margin-left: 10px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: #8b4513;
      color: white;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .back-btn {
      display: block;
      margin: 20px auto 0;
      background: #6b4f2a;
    }

    .music-note {
      margin-left: auto;
      font-size: 30px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .screen {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .main-title {
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .chat-input {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .chat-input button {
        margin-left: 0;
      }

      .message {
        max-width: 92%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section id="mainScreen" class="screen active">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1 class="main-title">🎼 시대별 클래식 음악가와 채팅하기 🎻</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">초등 음악 수업과 연결해서 배우는 클래식 체험관이에요 ✨<br>시대별 작곡가 사진을 누르면 채팅이 시작돼요</p>
    </div>

    <div id="eraContainer"></div>
  </section>

  <section id="chatScreen" class="screen">
    <div class="chat-container">
      <div class="chat-header">
        <img id="chatPhoto" src="" alt="음악가 사진">
        <div>
          <h2 id="chatName">음악가</h2>
          <p id="chatEra">시대</p>
        </div>
        <div class="music-note">🎼</div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning">⚠️ ⭐ 안내 ⭐ 이 대화 내용은 AI 학습용 예시 데이터로 만든 내용이라 실제 역사와 다를 수 있어요 🌈 중요한 내용은 선생님과 함께 다시 확인해요</div>

      <div class="quick-buttons">
        <button onclick="askQuick('대표곡에 대해 설명해줘')">🎵 대표곡</button>
        <button onclick="askQuick('이 시대 음악 특징은 뭐야?')">🏛️ 시대 특징</button>
        <button onclick="askQuick('어떤 사람이야?')">😊 어떤 사람?</button>
        <button onclick="askQuick('재미있는 이야기 알려줘')">✨ 재미있는 이야기</button>
        <button onclick="askQuick('퀴즈 내줘')">❓ 퀴즈</button>
      </div>

      <div id="chatBox" class="chat-box"></div>

      <div class="chat-input">
        <input id="userInput" type="text" placeholder="예: 바로크 음악이 뭐야? 대표곡에 대해 설명해줘" onkeydown="handleEnter(event)">
        <button onclick="sendMessage()">보내기</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button class="back-btn" onclick="goMain()">🏠 메인으로 돌아가기</button>
  </section>

